author: Unreal Engine
description:
SIMICO SPA’s Head of Digital Engineering Francesco Cappilli is here to talk about how Unreal Engine is helping power SimicoTwin, a digital twin platform that’s helping pioneer the future of sustainable infrastructure for the Milano Cortina 2026 Winter Olympics🎿

An Olympic level project requires an Olympic level talk, tomorrow at Unreal Fest Stockholm: http://epic.gm/unreal-fest-stockholm-agenda
title: Unreal Fest Stockholm Meet the Presenter: Francesco
